<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Feature 2 - Map Toggle</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ 'feature-2-map-slider.css' | asset_url }}">

  <!-- Google Maps JavaScript API -->
  <script async defer
    src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyCvbBZMdQ710YM1aSpZf8GGAQpBEnhMOi8&callback=initMap">
  </script>
</head>
<body>

  <h1 class="feature-2-map-slider-title">Feature 2 - Map Toggle</h1>

  <p class="feature-2-map-slider-description">
    Nam Hoang implementing feature 2 - map toggle for Greenfleet.
  </p>

  <div id="map-container">
    <div id="map"></div>
    <div class="toggle-container">
      <label class="switch">
        <input type="checkbox" id="toggleMarkers">
        <span class="slider round"></span>
      </label>
      <span class="toggle-label">Show Markers</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="{{ 'feature-2-map-slider.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
